Package ru.nsu.fit.smolyakov.recordbook.internal

Class Mark

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.fit.smolyakov.recordbook.internal.Mark
public class Mark extends Object
Provides a functionality to operate with marks specified in input JSON.

Implements a Mark constructor which takes Mark.Form of attestation and a value in range of 2 and 5 for Mark.Form.EXAM and Mark.Form.DIFFERENTIATED_CREDIT or "pass" or "fail" string literal for the Mark.Form.CREDIT, as well as static of(ru.nsu.fit.smolyakov.recordbook.internal.Mark.Form,java.lang.String) method to construct an instance.

Credits are not treated as valueable, so value method returns OptionalInt.empty() for them.
